WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:02.023
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:02.023 --> 00:00:04.354
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:04.354 --> 00:00:07.279
We're going to pray and sing a little bit.

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:12.559
I'll sing some songs or whatever the Lord has on His heart for me to sing.

00:00:12.559 --> 00:00:19.680
I woke up this morning singing a song out of my sleep, so I figured this is what He wanted to hear.

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:28.888
I told Diana, "You know, whenever it happens—it happens quite often—but this one, I haven't heard this song in so long and I couldn't believe it.

00:00:28.888 --> 00:00:31.440
I was like, 'Well, that's really cool.

00:00:31.440 --> 00:00:44.880
'" The last video was heavy, but I really feel in my spirit we've made great ground concerning praying for our president and praying for our nation.

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:54.987
I could feel the shifting last night as we were interceding for our leader, and that makes me so happy.

00:00:54.987 --> 00:00:57.200
It felt so good to feel that.

00:00:57.200 --> 00:01:11.469
For those of you familiar with what I'm talking about—some of you are just babies at this, but some of you are veterans—when you get in that river of prayer, you can feel the wall or you can feel a flow.

00:01:11.469 --> 00:01:17.840
Sometimes you just keep hitting that wall, hitting that door until you have it open.

00:01:18.870 --> 00:01:26.479
In prayer, a lot of times when I'm interceding, you can feel when other people are pulling with you.

00:01:26.479 --> 00:01:33.633
You can feel, in a corporate setting, when other people are on the same assignment as you in the Spirit.

00:01:33.633 --> 00:01:45.000
So, whenever I'm praying over our president and I'm praying over this, it's almost like you're walking through mud, and you're pulling and trying so hard to gain ground.

00:01:45.453 --> 00:01:52.704
You're grabbing and clenching and pulling yourself up out of it, and then all of a sudden, you're on a slide.

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:56.759
You could feel that last night as I was interceding.

00:02:01.897 --> 00:02:12.462
We had times of prayer here, and I want to tell you this: faith is not a feeling, and prayer is not a feeling.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:17.146
I'm not moved by what I see; I'm not moved by what I feel.

00:02:17.146 --> 00:02:20.480
I'm moved by what the Word of God says, so don't always go by a feeling.

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:25.020
But whenever you get sensitive to the things of the Spirit, you will know what I'm talking about more.

00:02:25.020 --> 00:02:30.819
There is a river, then there's dry, and then it's like going through mud.

00:02:30.819 --> 00:02:33.720
You can feel your toil in the ground; it's pulling and pulling.

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:42.080
Last night you could feel that there's so many people praying for President Trump and praying for this nation.

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:43.990
I was excited about it.

00:02:44.610 --> 00:02:51.440
I believe the fervent prayer of the righteous availeth much—the fervent, effectual prayer.

00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:58.259
Honey, find the scripture; I don't want to misquote it.

00:02:58.589 --> 00:03:07.154
I was looking at Proverbs 15:8: "The prayer of the upright is His delight.

00:03:07.668 --> 00:03:17.093
" I believe tonight, as we pray for our president and our nation, the prayer of the upright is His delight.

00:03:17.093 --> 00:03:18.387
Isn't that wonderful?

00:03:18.387 --> 00:03:22.640
I love that; He delights in it.

00:03:23.626 --> 00:03:28.879
James 5:16: "The effectual fervent prayer of a righteous man availeth much.

00:03:30.159 --> 00:03:37.599
" The fervent, effectual prayer of the righteous availeth much.

00:03:38.422 --> 00:03:40.480
We're getting the job done.

00:03:42.409 --> 00:03:49.480
I really believe that's what God has called and assigned us to do for such a time as this.

00:03:56.080 --> 00:03:59.840
The effectual fervent prayer of a righteous man availeth much.

00:04:00.347 --> 00:04:02.879
And that's who we are.

00:04:03.800 --> 00:04:06.133
Braden's grinning at me; I get tongue-tied.

00:04:09.382 --> 00:04:11.074
All glory to Jesus.

00:04:11.074 --> 00:04:12.227
Isn't that wonderful?

00:04:12.533 --> 00:04:26.589
I believe that's what we're doing and we'll continue to do all throughout 2026 and the rest of this year, praying over what I believe the Lord has shown us through prayer.

00:04:26.589 --> 00:04:34.250
We're praying over these major events where I believe we have power and authority.

00:04:34.250 --> 00:04:42.137
As we prayed into the storm and took authority over it, there wasn't as much damage as they were thinking.

00:04:42.137 --> 00:04:48.479
We didn't have as much snow as we were expecting.

00:04:50.460 --> 00:04:57.063
Maybe some people got a lot, but our area, when we got out today, didn't seem way bad.

00:04:57.063 --> 00:05:04.320
Based on what we could see on the news, it could have been a lot worse, with many more power outages.

00:05:09.170 --> 00:05:11.960
I believe it's because the people were praying.

00:05:12.260 --> 00:05:19.893
As big as that storm was and as big as that event could have been, it could have been more catastrophic.

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:23.680
So, we give all the glory to Jesus today.

00:05:24.571 --> 00:05:30.228
If you're without power, it's terrible, but I believe they'll get it on quickly.

00:05:30.228 --> 00:05:37.187
Let's pray that they get it on quickly tonight, that they'll have all the power up, and that you won't be without your electricity and heat.

00:05:37.940 --> 00:05:41.360
They'll be able to do a quick work and get to you fast.

00:05:42.213 --> 00:05:44.680
You'll have favor where everyone else doesn't.

00:05:45.187 --> 00:05:47.223
You'll have favor because you're a child of the King.

00:05:47.223 --> 00:05:55.190
I believe that God's favored you today and put goodness and mercy on you, and it's following you all the days of your life.

00:05:55.190 --> 00:05:58.023
I stand on that and we believe it.

00:05:58.023 --> 00:06:04.080
We're believing believers who are receivers, and we're contenders for the glory.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:13.480
We're contenders for the end-time anointing, the outpouring of finances, and whatever God has for us.

00:06:13.480 --> 00:06:15.800
We will lack no good thing.

00:06:16.250 --> 00:06:19.730
I believe that, so that's what we're going to stand on tonight.

00:06:20.020 --> 00:06:26.960
We see the things in the news from Carney, the Prime Minister of Canada.

00:06:29.919 --> 00:06:41.280
I thought it was interesting because of the prophetic words the Lord has given us and the visions we've seen about him going to China and saying, "Hey, I want to do business with you.

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:53.619
" This was his last major push, from what I saw in the Spirit, for his country to pull itself out of this hole.

00:06:53.969 --> 00:07:11.280
I saw Canada going into a depression and joining up with America in the days ahead—not saying Canada is dissolved, like I keep hearing President Trump saying '51st state' and all this, but a financial merger.

00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:15.480
Their currency became our currency; that's what I saw.

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:25.840
We still had borders, but their currency and Mexico's currency became one.

00:07:26.030 --> 00:07:29.599
This is what I've been praying over for two years.

00:07:30.099 --> 00:07:34.640
I think some things the Lord shows us happen really quickly, like the storm coming.

00:07:38.310 --> 00:07:41.973
We saw that back on November 11th, and we've been praying over it.

00:07:58.697 --> 00:07:59.028
We saw it on October 29th, and then we saw it again—was it in July?

00:07:59.028 --> 00:08:03.509
He's been talking to us about this for seven months.

00:08:03.509 --> 00:08:07.019
He talked about October and November, too.

00:08:07.019 --> 00:08:13.160
So, we've had these cues to pray over the weather and this storm.

00:08:26.559 --> 00:08:26.879
I believe we prayed over it and saw results.

00:08:26.879 --> 00:08:47.600
When we see Canada and Mexico joining up with the United States to have a currency, it's when I saw them trying to come against the dollar and the BRICS in the days ahead to bring a stronger currency system.

00:08:54.346 --> 00:08:54.640
We keep praying into that.

00:08:54.640 --> 00:09:06.667
All I know is it's all leading up to the Mark of the Beast and the One World Order.

00:09:20.942 --> 00:09:21.138
What will be the lynchpin for the One World Order and the one-world currency?

00:09:40.789 --> 00:09:41.120
I believe truly—and this is just Braden and me thinking, I can't speak for Diana, though I know she agrees with everything—the Rapture of the Church could be the lynchpin.

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:56.187
The total meltdown of society will happen when hundreds of millions, if not a billion, believers are taken out of here in the Rapture of the Church.

00:09:56.187 --> 00:10:08.027
Now, there are a lot of people who don't believe that, but I'm trying to say: what is the lynchpin that pushes this over?

00:10:08.027 --> 00:10:12.736
War, rumors of war, plague.

00:10:12.736 --> 00:10:22.960
The plague that I've seen coming in 2020, 2028, the spring and fall of 2027, going into 2028, is when I've seen a great shaking coming.

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:25.039
Now, some people say that's too early, Brandon.

00:10:28.178 --> 00:10:28.427
I believe that it's further down the road.

00:10:32.460 --> 00:10:32.720
I believe we're going to see an economic crisis before we see the plague.

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:38.420
This is what I saw when I was praying: the financial and economic situation and the plague go hand in hand.

00:10:38.420 --> 00:10:40.512
They ride together.

00:10:40.512 --> 00:10:43.131
They're like twins.

00:10:43.131 --> 00:10:45.886
Famine and plague ride together.

00:10:49.730 --> 00:10:52.569
And so, you know, that's just me looking into it.

00:10:52.569 --> 00:10:57.820
I don't want to add to or take away from anything.

00:10:57.820 --> 00:11:08.960
It's just me trying to figure it out with my natural mind and say, "Listen, Lord, how close are you to your coming?

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:12.415
How close are we?

00:11:12.415 --> 00:11:20.300
" There are a lot of people who believe He could come back in the next five minutes.

00:11:23.279 --> 00:11:25.840
I believe no man knows the day or the hour; that's what the Bible says.

00:11:30.779 --> 00:11:31.029
But we can see the signs of the times looking all around us.

00:11:31.029 --> 00:11:44.169
We see Iran and all the uprisings and the regime change that I believe is about to happen in Cuba, Mexico, and so on, as part of this end-time move.

00:11:44.169 --> 00:12:02.959
Here we see some people are saying, "Is this the ten kings rising up in Gaza with the president and Jared Kushner running this, and the new Gaza Strip and all the beauty of the buildings that they're promising?

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:08.666
" And they have oil derricks, and they put that off to the side, a little bit over here.

00:12:22.760 --> 00:12:23.200
I thought that was interesting.

00:12:36.389 --> 00:12:36.639
The beautiful landscape I told you looked like Miami; that's what I saw in the spirit.

00:12:44.800 --> 00:12:45.240
And the Lord said, "But I saw oil, oil, oil and gas, gas, gas.

00:12:45.240 --> 00:12:52.440
" I said there was so much money, billions of dollars in the Mediterranean, outside of Gaza.

00:13:08.300 --> 00:13:08.590
I saw so much money down in there.

00:13:08.590 --> 00:13:14.320
It was a pocket of oil that was one of the largest reserves in the world.

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:21.620
And the Lord said, "I put that there strategically for my people.

00:13:28.639 --> 00:13:29.039
It's been there and they're about to tap into it.

00:13:29.039 --> 00:13:39.417
" Well, maybe they've tapped into a little bit of it, but I believe that God is able to replenish and bring it in.

00:13:52.230 --> 00:13:52.460
It could not have been there and all of a sudden, He's like, "You know what?

00:13:54.359 --> 00:13:55.920
" And the oil goes, and you go, "How in the world?

00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:56.738
" It's only God.

00:13:56.738 --> 00:13:58.840
That's why I believe we're so close.

00:13:58.840 --> 00:14:02.960
We're about to see something major.

00:14:04.480 --> 00:14:11.531
As we pray, keep praying into 2026 as this valley of decision where President Trump is at right now.

00:14:27.058 --> 00:14:27.333
Just like the Lord told us back at the first of January, He said he's going to go through the valley of decision.

00:14:27.333 --> 00:14:34.184
His decisions are going to fork off, and he'll either go this way or he'll go that way.

00:14:34.184 --> 00:14:42.423
But it's up to the church to pray him through this so that he makes the right decisions.

00:14:51.048 --> 00:14:51.351
The Bible says, "Choose life.

00:14:51.351 --> 00:14:54.800
" Life and death are in the power of...

00:14:54.800 --> 00:14:55.600
choose life.

00:15:09.261 --> 00:15:09.670
I don't know if I'm quoting that scripture right again, but He's talking about choosing life.

00:15:09.670 --> 00:15:10.769
It's your choice.

00:15:10.769 --> 00:15:14.420
Choose the direction of what I want you to have.

00:15:14.420 --> 00:15:15.409
Choose life.

00:15:15.409 --> 00:15:16.719
It's a choice.

00:15:41.616 --> 00:15:42.432
So we pray for President Trump to make the right choice.

00:15:42.432 --> 00:15:45.190
It's so important.

00:15:45.190 --> 00:15:50.525
You don't realize how much authority you have as a believing believer.

00:16:07.440 --> 00:16:07.771
That's the problem.

00:16:07.771 --> 00:16:15.542
A lot of the church doesn't realize that when Christ sat down, we sat down with Him.

00:16:15.542 --> 00:16:18.354
As He is, so are we in this world.

00:16:18.354 --> 00:16:20.970
Ephesians is alive, and it's alive in me.

00:16:27.737 --> 00:16:35.199
The more you read it, the more it's going to renew your mind, and the more you're going to get the Word inside of you and it will change you from the inside out.

00:16:35.199 --> 00:16:51.079
When you become God-inspired, God-thinking—as He is, so are we in this world—you have to be a believing believer who receives it by reading this Bible and getting it down in your heart.

00:16:51.079 --> 00:16:56.148
Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the Word of God.

00:17:08.338 --> 00:17:08.542
The only way you're going to change, ladies and gentlemen, is by getting this Word down inside of your heart.

00:17:20.924 --> 00:17:21.209
You can read it and just glance over it, but it's when you meditate on it, when you get it down inside of you, that the entrance of the Word brings forth light.

00:17:24.640 --> 00:17:24.880
The Word will change you and bring forth light.

00:17:24.880 --> 00:17:28.559
That's what I'm trying to tell you all tonight.

00:17:36.667 --> 00:17:37.000
You must get this Word down inside of you for just what we read: the fervent, effectual prayer.

00:17:39.493 --> 00:17:40.240
What does it mean to be fervent?

00:17:42.685 --> 00:17:49.760
To be fervent means to probably be like a bulldog on a bone—one who is passionate about prayer.

00:17:54.738 --> 00:17:59.644
We probably could look up the definition of it, Diana, but I just visualize what the Lord is saying.

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:09.200
The fervent, effectual prayer of the righteous.

00:18:09.680 --> 00:18:16.800
When you are just dogmatic—I am going to get it, we're going to believe God—having displayed a passion of intensity.

00:18:16.800 --> 00:18:22.050
Thank you, Braden and Diana, my two helpers.

00:18:22.050 --> 00:18:26.880
"Having or displaying a passionate intensity.

00:18:39.129 --> 00:18:39.307
" So, just being intense.

00:18:39.307 --> 00:18:41.320
That's what we are; we're intense.

00:18:41.320 --> 00:18:46.799
I want to be all in for Jesus, being sold out.

00:18:46.799 --> 00:18:54.809
I want to be filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit so that when people see me, they say, "He's intense.

00:19:04.520 --> 00:19:04.880
" I like that.

00:19:04.880 --> 00:19:06.320
He's intense; he's passionate.

00:19:06.320 --> 00:19:12.103
He's not just somebody who says, "Oh well, whatever will be, will be.

00:19:25.573 --> 00:19:25.777
" I believe that we're the people who say, "No, we can change things through faith.

00:19:28.480 --> 00:19:36.720
We can speak to our mountain, 'Be thou removed, be thou cast into the sea,' and we shall not doubt in our hearts.

00:19:50.760 --> 00:19:51.120
We shall have whatsoever things we say.

00:19:51.120 --> 00:19:56.693
" Mark 11:24, we're going to speak to the mountain.

00:19:57.428 --> 00:20:01.200
This is the mountain of where we are right now.

00:20:07.280 --> 00:20:07.520
We have President Trump and he has counsel.

00:20:09.819 --> 00:20:20.640
We need to pray for godly counsel around him to make godly decisions concerning Greenland, Iran, Cuba, Mexico—all these things where he could put his influence, being from the strongest nation in the world, being able to influence and bring forth the end-time harvest.

00:20:20.640 --> 00:20:28.309
Where could we, as believing believers, help influence by praying over him to have good, godly counsel?

00:20:28.309 --> 00:20:35.733
Not having evil people speaking into his life who say, "Well, we want to go this way," when it's not the plan of the Lord.

00:20:49.716 --> 00:20:50.124
The plan of the Lord is to bring all that is lost to be saved.

00:20:50.124 --> 00:20:54.600
He wills that no one should perish, but all come to repentance.

00:21:00.542 --> 00:21:00.817
But everybody has to have ears to hear, plus they have to have a way to hear it.

00:21:00.817 --> 00:21:15.497
If you have a dictator over an area and they say, "Well, we don't want the Bible coming in here; we don't want Christianity being preached.

00:21:19.806 --> 00:21:24.000
" The Bible says when this Word is preached as a witness throughout the whole world, then the end will come.

00:21:24.000 --> 00:21:28.880
So is that a restrainer—whenever you can't hear the Word?

00:21:28.880 --> 00:21:29.484
Yes.

00:21:29.484 --> 00:21:35.226
So what do we do with the restrainer trying to prevent bringing the Word into the nation?

00:21:36.616 --> 00:21:45.819
We remove it by faith, by prayer, by fasting, and by coming into agreement through corporate prayer, saying, "No, we will have a revival in Cuba.

00:21:52.640 --> 00:21:52.960
We will have a revival in Brazil, in Iran, and North Korea.

00:21:52.960 --> 00:21:56.330
" Those people are being oppressed.

00:21:56.330 --> 00:22:00.640
They're suppressed and they can't get out; they have an iron curtain there.

00:22:03.565 --> 00:22:07.039
But when we are believing believers who come into agreement, we can move that out of the way.

00:22:07.039 --> 00:22:08.583
That's why we're here.

00:22:10.040 --> 00:22:13.279
I just want you to get excited about prayer.

00:22:13.279 --> 00:22:15.080
Be that definition—passionate intensity.

00:22:15.080 --> 00:22:17.840
It's time; we've got to do it.

00:22:17.840 --> 00:22:21.573
That's what we're here for today.

00:22:26.459 --> 00:22:27.239
I like that.

00:22:43.280 --> 00:22:43.499
The prayer of the upright is his delight.

00:22:43.499 --> 00:22:46.540
So we have prayers and we are upright.

00:22:46.540 --> 00:22:51.664
We are the righteousness of God in Christ Jesus.

00:22:51.664 --> 00:22:57.467
Every single one of us here, we take it by faith.

00:22:57.467 --> 00:22:59.623
We're wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

00:22:59.623 --> 00:23:09.661
He dwells on the inside of us and we take this communion and all the things that we see on the news.

00:23:09.661 --> 00:23:15.220
Like I said a thousand times, if you're praying the news, you're too late.

00:23:15.220 --> 00:23:18.347
We see the news before the news happens.

00:23:18.347 --> 00:23:25.188
We can turn this thing before the news manifests.

00:23:25.188 --> 00:23:31.851
Terrorist attacks, the Red Dawn experience, volcanoes.

00:23:31.851 --> 00:23:33.680
People say, 'Where's the volcano, Brandon?

00:23:33.680 --> 00:23:36.170
How come we haven't seen a volcano?

00:23:36.170 --> 00:23:39.053
' I want to be real with you.

00:23:39.053 --> 00:23:46.479
From what I saw, we see the beginning stages of something shaking in the ground outside of Oregon's coast.

00:23:46.479 --> 00:23:47.947
Those are warning signs.

00:24:11.290 --> 00:24:11.700
It's 6.

00:24:11.700 --> 00:24:12.520
0.

00:24:27.837 --> 00:24:28.875
The ground is shaking in the deep just like the Lord said it would in the exact spot the Lord told us it would.

00:24:28.875 --> 00:24:36.300
But you say, 'Well, how come it hasn't happened and nobody's died?

00:24:36.300 --> 00:24:39.200
' Because we have prayers out there.

00:24:39.200 --> 00:24:48.960
I believe that's a prayer foil if we start seeing this stuff happen to the capacity against our believing brothers and sisters.

00:24:48.960 --> 00:24:55.159
I believe a thousand shall fall at your side, 10,000 at your right hand, folks.

00:24:55.159 --> 00:24:59.066
But we know we're in the end times.

00:24:59.066 --> 00:25:02.880
We're going to see some things.

00:25:02.880 --> 00:25:06.297
We can't stop it all.

00:25:06.297 --> 00:25:11.455
But those are the signs I'm trying to tell you.

00:25:11.455 --> 00:25:13.096
It's in the ground.

00:25:13.096 --> 00:25:14.827
It's happening right there.

00:25:14.827 --> 00:25:22.986
How much more do you need to see other than a catastrophic event killing a whole bunch of people?

00:25:36.319 --> 00:25:36.559
And we don't want that.

00:25:51.440 --> 00:25:51.840
It's in the ground.

00:25:51.840 --> 00:25:53.632
It's in the water.

00:25:53.632 --> 00:25:54.208
It's signs.

00:26:20.205 --> 00:26:20.468
And the Lord said, 'Watch the fish coming up out of the water and coming up on the shores.

00:26:20.468 --> 00:26:27.422
' And this will be a sign that it's about ready to happen.

00:26:27.422 --> 00:26:30.120
We're already seeing precursors of it.

00:26:30.120 --> 00:26:33.417
Major earthquakes, major shakings, major awakenings, wars, and rumors of wars.

00:26:33.417 --> 00:26:35.549
We are in the last days.

00:26:35.549 --> 00:26:49.229
But I think it's interesting, like a frog in a pot, the water is getting hotter and hotter and hotter, and people around it get so accustomed to what they're seeing all the time.

00:26:54.027 --> 00:27:01.120
But if you go back 20 years ago to the early 2000s and you were to go and look ahead, you would go, 'Oh my gosh, this is definitely the end times.

00:27:01.120 --> 00:27:17.102
